</section>

<!-- WHO I AM + STYLES + AUDIENCE -->
<section>
  <div class="wrap">

    <div class="who-grid rev">
      <div>
        <span class="sec-label">Hey, I'm Chris</span>
        <div class="sec-title">HIRE THE GUY<br>WHO'S<br><em>ALREADY THERE.</em></div>
      </div>
      <div class="who-body">
        <p>I got into UGC because I was already living the kind of life the brands I love were trying to market. I surf. I biohack. I travel carry-on only. When I create content for a brand that fits that world — it's placed inside a <strong>real life, in real locations, with real reactions.</strong> Your audience can tell the difference. That's the whole point.</p>
        <p>I specialize in <strong>Meta whitelisting and Partnership Ads</strong> — content built to run as paid ads through my account. Your budget, my audience trust. That combination is the highest-converting short-form format running right now. And because my content is built around <strong>authentic lifestyle moments</strong>, it doesn't feel like an ad — even when it is.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Editorial photo splash: Chris portrait + surf van -->
