        <div class="style-card" data-num="02"><div class="sc-icon">🌊</div><div class="sc-name">Travel & Location</div><div class="sc-desc">Shot on location in Bali, Costa Rica, Miami, Amsterdam. Your brand inside the world your customer dreams about.</div><div class="sc-fit">Travel Gear · Hotels · Lifestyle</div></div>
        <div class="style-card" data-num="03"><div class="sc-icon">🎤</div><div class="sc-name">Direct-to-Camera</div><div class="sc-desc">Honest, confident, no teleprompter energy. A friend telling you about something they genuinely use.</div><div class="sc-fit">Any product solving a real problem</div></div>
