        <div class="style-card" data-num="05"><div class="sc-icon">💬</div><div class="sc-name">"Guy Who Has It Together"</div><div class="sc-desc">Identity-based POV. Your product becomes part of who they want to become — not just something they buy.</div><div class="sc-fit">Men's Health · Supplements · Tools</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- VIDEO REEL with photo thumbnails -->
<section class="reel-section" id="reel">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="reel-top rev">
      <div>
        <span class="sec-label">Content Reel</span>
        <div class="sec-title" style="margin-bottom:0;">LIGHTS. CAMERA.<br><em>CONVERSION.</em></div>
      </div>
      <span class="reel-note">Click any video to play</span>
    </div>
    <div class="vgrid rev">
<div class="vi" onclick="playV(this)">
